{"tid":1354066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【元朗襲擊】區議員：事前曾要求增警力不果","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:14:48.000Z","uid":173011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c0ea3fc8edfe8f4fb976567499c47aef58b27e","tid":1354066,"uid":173011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356414&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356414%26refer%3DShare&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQZa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=519d7087\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356414%26refer%3DShare&h=a41d3538\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356414&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【元朗襲擊】區議員：事前曾要求增警力不果<br />\n<br />\n1小時前&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n觀看新聞片段<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】元朗周日發生暴力襲擊事件，有元朗區議員指事前已經有迹象顯示出現混亂，曾經聯絡警方要求增加警力，但警方並無行動回應。有區議員則指，曾聽到有中聯辦官員呼籲原居民不要讓示威者到元朗生事。<br />\n<br />\n元朗周日發生暴力襲擊，有一群白衣人士在元朗西鐵站及附近商場襲擊市民。元朗區議員王威信出席本台節目《時事全方位》指，事發前已聯絡警方，並要求增加警力不果。<br />\n<br />\n另一名元朗區議員黃偉賢就指，在元朗暴力事件前幾天，即上周四在鄉事委員會活動上，有中聯辦官員呼籲原居民不要讓反修例的示威者到元朗生事。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，其間曾聯絡警方並要求派警員到場處理事件，但三小時後仍沒有警員到場維待秩序。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"93fb576daa6d1bb0afea3edb505243443b20390b","tid":1354066,"uid":285746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:54:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/origos2014/photos/a.715971415105219/2301143473254664/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Forigos2014%2Fphotos%2Fa.715971415105219%2F2301143473254664%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQZa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=cb7f8929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/origos2014/photos/a.715971415105219/2301143473254664/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"c